[ php2py - converter from php to python using phc ]
----------------------------------------------------------------------
php2py is a php script to convert php to python.
As input, this script accept syntax tree XML file generated by phc
instead of php code.

[ Requirements ]
----------------------------------------------------------------------
php2py.php requires "phc" (php compiler) installed.
you can download it at the following link:

https://github.com/pbiggar/phc

[ Example Use ]
----------------------------------------------------------------------
$ phc --dump-xml=ast somecode.php > out.xml
$ ./php2py.php out.xml > somecode.py
